EPISODE 17

3
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:51,720
Shancai, look.

4
00:01:52,160 --> 00:01:55,400
The photos taken in Canada received
a lot of likes after they were shared.

5
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:56,400
