8
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:03,720
"Someone's forgotten this friend."

9
00:02:04,240 --> 00:02:06,280
-I'll reply.
-What will you say?

10
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:09,200
"You're a pet."

11
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:11,000
