the dragon you had before.

123
00:07:38,880 --> 00:07:39,800
That's right.

124
00:07:40,440 --> 00:07:42,840
Zhibu's beast doesn't even have a takedown

125
00:07:43,080 --> 00:07:44,600
but he leveled up to 70.

126
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:46,240
