-Come on.

149
00:08:41,880 --> 00:08:43,320
Come on.

150
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:44,280
Come get me.

151
00:08:44,800 --> 00:08:45,640
Here.

152
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:51,200
Yeah.

153
00:08:52,160 --> 00:08:53,000
Okay.

154
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:54,880
I admit defeat, okay?

155
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:58,880
