156
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:02,560
Let's punish Zhibu who started it.

157
00:09:02,880 --> 00:09:03,880
I'm okay with that.

158
00:09:05,040 --> 00:09:06,120
Qinghe too.

159
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,160
What?

160
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:14,720
