177
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:05,160
We didn't invite anyone to Canada.

178
00:10:05,400 --> 00:10:06,880
Xinhui and Baihe came along.

179
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:08,640
Many people are complaining.

180
00:10:09,520 --> 00:10:11,000
