Is there any problem?

235
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:05,000
-Shancai has a boyfriend?
-Yeah.

236
00:13:05,080 --> 00:13:06,440
-Really?
-I didn't know.

237
00:13:06,520 --> 00:13:07,920
-Since when?
-She's dating?

238
00:13:08,160 --> 00:13:10,000
-Shancai's boyfriend is handsome.
-Is he?

239
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:11,040
